data.description: This meticulously kept spacious rambler welcomes you with soaring ceilings. As you are greeted by an oversized kitchen featuring granite slab and high end appliances,  with eating area that connects to dining room and living room, the quality of in  craftmanship is felt throughout the home. Enjoy the flowing floorplan, accentuated by natural light of the large windows and skylights.  Closet organizers in every closet allow organization and maximize space. Enjoy the cozy fireplace in the fall, plus the a/c will keep you comfortably cool in the summer. Rolling gates allow for easy access of boat, and/or RV w/ 30 amp (space for both!). Wired for generator, upgraded panel with space to add EV charging. Shed stays. New HWT in 2022.
